{q:"What 'most precious gift' can volcanologists give people?", opts:["The power to stop eruptions","Enough warning time to escape","Free electricity","Richer farmland"], a:1, ex:"By predicting eruptions they give people 'enough time to escape' — they cannot stop a volcano."},
{q:"What is the main purpose of this passage?", opts:["To persuade people to move away from volcanoes","To tell an exciting story about Pompeii","To explain how volcanoes form and why they matter","To describe the life of a volcanologist"], a:2, ex:"It is an informative text explaining what causes volcanoes and their effects, both harmful and helpful."}
